creator: Bolt Technology
descriptionHtml:
Bolt is a transportation app used for requesting a fast and affordable ride.
Use your smartphone to order a ride, get picked up by a nearby driver, and enjoy a low-cost trip to your destination.

Why choose Bolt?
• Get a comfortable, low-cost ride
• Fast arrival times, 24/7
• All Bolt rides in Europe are 100% carbon-neutral
• See the price of your ride before you order
• You can pay inside the app (Credit/Debit/Apple Pay)

Easily request a ride with the Bolt app:
1. Open the app and set your destination;
2. Request a driver to pick you up;
3. See your driver's location on the real-time map;
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination;
5. Leave a rating and pay.

Bolt is available in 30+ countries and 150+ cities around the world.

Bolt’s mission is to bring fast, reliable and affordable transportation to millions of people around the world, while also helping thousands of drivers support their families. The next time you need a ride, take Bolt!

Earn extra money driving with Bolt. Sign up at https://partners.bolt.eu

Questions? Get in touch via info@bolt.eu or at https://bolt.eu

Follow us on social media for updates, discounts and offers!

title: Bolt

creator: Bolt Technology
descriptionHtml:
Bolt is a ride-hailing app for requesting a fast and affordable ride.

Just tap the button to order a ride, get picked up by a nearby driver, and enjoy a low-cost ride to your destination.


How to request a ride with the Bolt app:

1. Open the app and set your destination
2. Request a driver to pick you up
3. See your driver arrive in real-time
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination
5. Pay in-app or in cash (available in select countries)

Bolt app features:

• See the ride price upfront, and know how much you will pay
• The app helps to set your pickup location even if you don't know the exact address
• You can rate your driver to give feedback and help us improve the service quality
• Add your credit card and never worry about carrying cash again. We'll email you the receipt after every trip

Bolt is available in 30+ countries and 100+ cities around the world.

Bolt’s mission is to bring fast and accessible transport to millions of people around the world, while helping thousands of drivers support their families. The next time you need a ride, take Bolt!

Earn extra money with your car. Sign up as a driver: https://partners.bolt.eu

Have questions? Get in touch via info@bolt.eu or at https://bolt.eu

Like us on Facebook https://facebook.com/bolt
Follow us on Twitter https://twitter.com/boltapp

title: Bolt: Fast, Affordable Rides

creator: Bolt Technology
descriptionHtml:
Use your smartphone to order a ride, get picked up by a nearby driver, and enjoy a low-cost trip to your destination.

Why choose Bolt?
• Get a comfortable, low-cost ride.
• Fast arrival times, 24/7.
• All Bolt rides in Europe are 100% carbon-neutral.
• See the price of your ride before you order.
• You can pay inside the app (Credit/Debit/Apple Pay).

Easily request a ride with the Bolt app:
1. Open the app and set your destination;
2. Request a driver to pick you up;
3. See your driver's location on the real-time map;
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination;
5. Leave a rating and pay.

Bolt is available in 30+ countries and 150+ cities around the world.

Bolt’s mission is to bring fast, reliable and affordable transportation to millions of people around the world, while also helping thousands of drivers support their families. The next time you need a ride, take Bolt!

title: Bolt: Fast, Affordable Rides

creator: Bolt Technology
descriptionHtml:
Use your smartphone to order a ride, get picked up by a nearby driver, and enjoy a low-cost trip to your destination.

Why choose Bolt?
• Get a comfortable, low-cost ride.
• Fast arrival times, 24/7.
• All Bolt rides in Europe are 100% carbon-neutral.
• See the price of your ride before you order.
• You can pay inside the app (Credit/Debit/Apple Pay).

Easily request a ride with the Bolt app:
1. Open the app and set your destination;
2. Request a driver to pick you up;
3. See your driver's location on the real-time map;
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination;
5. Leave a rating and pay.

Bolt is available in 30+ countries and 150+ cities around the world.

Bolt’s mission is to bring fast, reliable and affordable transportation to millions of people around the world, while also helping thousands of drivers support their families. The next time you need a ride, take Bolt!

Earn extra money driving with Bolt. Sign up at https://partners.bolt.eu

Questions? Get in touch via info@bolt.eu or at https://bolt.eu

Follow us on social media for updates, discounts and offers!

title: Bolt: Fast, Affordable Rides

creator: Bolt Technology
descriptionHtml:
Use your smartphone to order a ride, get picked up by a nearby driver, and enjoy a low-cost trip to your destination.

Why choose Bolt?
• Get a comfortable, low-cost ride.
• Fast arrival times, 24/7.
• All Bolt rides in Europe are 100% carbon-neutral.
• See the price of your ride before you order.
• You can pay inside the app (Credit/Debit/Apple Pay).

Easily request a ride with the Bolt app:
1. Open the app and set your destination;
2. Request a driver to pick you up;
3. See your driver's location on the real-time map;
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination;
5. Leave a rating and pay.

Bolt is available in 30+ countries and 150+ cities around the world.

Bolt’s mission is to bring fast, reliable and affordable transportation to millions of people around the world, while also helping thousands of drivers support their families. The next time you need a ride, take Bolt!

Earn extra money driving with Bolt. Sign up at https://partners.bolt.eu

Questions? Get in touch via info@bolt.eu or at https://bolt.eu

Follow us on social media for updates, discounts and offers!

Instagram — https://www.instagram.com/bolt_uk/
Twitter — https://twitter.com/Boltapp

Use your smartphone to order a ride, get picked up by a nearby driver, and enjoy a low-cost trip to your destination.

Why choose Bolt?
• Get a comfortable, low-cost ride.
• Fast arrival times, 24/7.
• See the price of your ride before you order.
• You can pay inside the app (Credit/Debit/Apple Pay).

Easily request a ride with the Bolt app:
1. Open the app and set your destination;
2. Request a driver to pick you up;
3. See your driver's location on the real-time map;
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination;
5. Leave a rating and pay.

Bolt is available in 45 countries and 400 cities around the world.

Bolt’s mission is to bring fast, reliable and affordable transportation to millions of people around the world, while also helping thousands of drivers support their families. The next time you need a ride, take Bolt!

Earn extra money driving with Bolt. Sign up at https://partners.bolt.eu

Questions? Get in touch via info@bolt.eu or at https://bolt.eu

Follow us on social media for updates, discounts and offers!

Facebook — https://www.facebook.com/BoltUnitedKingdom/
Instagram — https://www.instagram.com/bolt_uk/
Twitter — https://twitter.com/Boltapp
descriptionShort: Bolt is a transport app used for requesting a fast and affordable ride.

All Bolt rides in Europe are 100% carbon neutral.

title: Bolt: Request a Ride

creator: Bolt Technology
descriptionHtml:
Use your smartphone to order a ride, get picked up by a nearby driver, and enjoy a low-cost trip to your destination.

Why choose Bolt?
• Get a comfortable, low-cost ride.
• Fast arrival times, 24/7.
• See the price of your ride before you order.
• You can pay inside the app (Credit/Debit/Apple Pay).

Easily request a ride with the Bolt app:
1. Open the app and set your destination;
2. Request a driver to pick you up;
3. See your driver's location on the real-time map;
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination;
5. Leave a rating and pay.

Bolt is available in 45 countries and 400 cities around the world.

Bolt’s mission is to bring fast, reliable and affordable transportation to millions of people around the world, while also helping thousands of drivers support their families. The next time you need a ride, take Bolt!

Earn extra money driving with Bolt. Sign up at https://partners.bolt.eu

title: Bolt: Request a Ride

creator: Bolt Technology
descriptionHtml:
Need a ride? We'll be there in minutes.

Bolt is the super app you need to move around town. Our top-rated drivers arrive in minutes to take you wherever you need to go, and our industry-leading scooters are always around the corner if you want to avoid traffic.

Why Bolt?
• The average arrival time of our drivers is just 3 minutes.
• The average rating of our drivers is 4.7 / 5 stars.
• Our scooters are packed with safety features to ensure a smooth, safe ride.
• We serve over 110 million customers in more than 500 cities and 45+ countries across 4 continents.
• We neutralise all CO2 emissions that your rides generate.
• We regularly send personalised promo offers.

How to request a ride with the Bolt smartphone app:
1. Open the app and set your destination;
2. Request a pick up by a Bolt driver;
3. Track your driver's location on the real-time map;
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination;
5. Pay and rate your ride — it helps us improve.

Whether you need a ride to work, a hassle-free airport transfer, or a premium car for a special night out — choose Bolt and improve how you move!

At Bolt, we believe that the key to better cities lies in how we move around them. By offering alternative modes of transport to the private car, we aim to reduce congestion, limit air and noise pollution and decrease the number of accidents on our roads. Thank you for helping us get there.

Learn more about our mission at bolt.eu

Questions? Get in touch at info@bolt.eu

Earn extra money driving with Bolt! Sign up at https://partners.bolt.eu

Follow us on social media for updates, discounts and offers!

Instagram — https://www.instagram.com/bolt
Twitter — https://twitter.com/Boltapp

2. Request a driver to pick you up;
3. See your driver's location on the real-time map;

Bolt features that require the app to stay running in the foreground:

• VoIP calls. Users can utilise in-app calls for communication to help locate each other or if a passenger forgets something in the car, for example.

title:
Bolt: Request a Ride
CA.127.0

creator: Bolt Technology
descriptionHtml:
Use your smartphone to order a ride, get picked up by a nearby driver, and enjoy a low-cost trip to your destination.

Why choose Bolt?
• Get a comfortable, low-cost ride.
• Fast arrival times, 24/7.
• See the price of your ride before you order.
• You can pay inside the app (Credit/Debit/Apple Pay).

Easily request a ride with the Bolt app:
1. Open the app and set your destination;
2. Request a driver to pick you up;
3. See your driver's location on the real-time map;
4. Enjoy the ride to your destination;
5. Leave a rating and pay.

Bolt features that require the app to stay running in the foreground:
• SOS button. In case of an incident, the user can easily provide their live location to a safety provider to get help faster.
• Trip audio recording. Users have the ability to record the trip audio if they feel unsafe or are facing a complicated situation. This audio can be used as evidence for investigations by the authorities.
• VoIP calls. Users can utilise in-app calls for communication to help locate each other or if a passenger forgets something in the car, for example.

*We're dedicated to fostering greener cities, which is why we're continually looking to increase our lineup of electric and hybrid cars in our car-sharing offering, Bolt Drive. You can also rent Bolt scooters and electric bikes via the app.

Bolt is available in 50 countries and 600+ cities around the world.

*Bolt scooter and car rental options differ by location. Check the app for availability in your city.

Bolt’s mission is to bring fast, reliable and affordable transportation to millions of people around the world, while also helping thousands of drivers support their families. The next time you need a ride, take Bolt!

Earn extra money driving with Bolt. Sign up at https://bolt.eu/en/driver/

Bolt features that require the app to stay running in the background:

• Private phone details: When a rider makes a call via our app, the caller’s phone number remains hidden.

*We're dedicated to fostering greener cities, which is why we're continually looking to increase our lineup of electric and hybrid cars in our car-sharing offering, Bolt Drive. You can also rent Bolt scooters and electric bikes via the app.
